Output unbrk-recover.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1200
Set Height 400
Set Padding 30
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set TypingSpeed 3ms

Type "./unbrk recover --port /dev/ttyUSB3 --preloader ~/dev/tftp/prplos-airoha-an7581-nokia_valyrian-preloader.bin --fip ~/dev/tftp/prplos-airoha-an7581-nokia_valyrian-bl31-uboot.fip"
Enter
Sleep 7s
Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
